tools.description:
Get the list of column names and their types for a given dataset.

Args:
    dataset_name (str): The unique name of the dataset.

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": {
            "columns": List[str],
            "schema": Dict[str, str]
        }
    }
    or {
        "success": False,
        "error": str
    }

Constraints:
    - Dataset with the given name must exist.
